reviewText: Fun lyrics and catchy toons.  I believe this video will catch the attention of a room full of toddlers.  Full of praise and worship songs little ones are able to repeat.

I purchased a number of Miss Patty Cake DVD's when my daughter was 1-2 years old.  She absolutely loved watching them. They engaged her.  There is music, movement, and a wholesome message.  She is 3 1/2 now and watches them less but she absolutely adored them - I had them all memorized myself because she would watch them over and over.  She still sings some of the Miss Patty Cake songs.  Miss Patty Cake DVDs are great.
